name: Green Squadron 1 (V)
Lore: 'Constructed at Chardaan Shipyards, a zero-gravity facility. Typically used as an escort for Y-wings or B-wings on critical attack missions.',
Text: 'May add Green Leader as a pilot. Once per turn, may take Diversionary Tactics into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If with Executor at end of battle, may draw destiny; Executor and this starfighter lost if destiny > 5.',
